a.n: TECHNO-SCIENCE - IMPACTO DEL HOMBRE EN VESTIGIOS MILENARIOS

p.k: In this chapter, Andrea goes to San Vicente de Tagua Tagua to see a museum of natural history. Research shows that the sector Tagua Tagua million years ago was under the ocean, and found fossils of shellfish and other marine species. In the Cerro La Muralla they discover daily evidence that show the data of the first settlers addition to the extinction of the gongoferios.
